0. only proceed if you have a light sensor on device
	- tip: light sensor is available if you have auto brightness feature

1. go to bin, install the apk file (or even better, fire a pull request, update, generate a better apk)

2. Connect to the network where the server is running (refer django-sensor-server repo)

3. provide a name in the UI and the server url 

4. click on post data to send data to server

5. check the sent data at /post/monitor 